title: Air Fryer Scrambled Eggs On The Go

Ingredients.3: 1 salt and freshly ground black pepper to taste

Directions.1: Lightly spray a ramekin dish with non-stick cooking spray. Pour in beaten eggs.

Directions.2: Set air fryer to 370 degrees F (185 degrees C) and place the ramekin into the air fryer basket.

Directions.3: Air fry for 3 minutes. Stir egg mixture and cook for 3 minutes more. Fluff with a fork and season to taste with salt and pepper. Grab and go.
